---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Leadership & Financial Freedom"
  description="Jason Ehlinger — Leadership coach and personal finance expert. Built a 7-figure business from scratch. Helping you lead better and build wealth."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Leadership · Finance · Freedom</span>
      <h1>Your Team Isn't Broken.<br/><em>Your Leadership System Is.</em></h1>
      <p>I built a 7-figure company from a card table in our living room — no investors, no trust fund. Now I teach the exact frameworks I used to lead high-performing teams and build lasting wealth.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-gold">Explore Services</a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">My Story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOCIAL PROOF BAR -->
  <section style="background:#111; padding:1.5rem; border-bottom:1px solid #222;">
    <div class="container" style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:2rem; justify-content:center; align-items:center;">
      <div style="text-align:center; color:#ccc;">
        <strong style="color:#fff; display:block; font-size:1.4rem;">7-Figure</strong>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase;">Business Built</span>
      </div>
      <div style="width:1px; height:40px; background:#333;"></div>
      <div style="text-align:center; color:#ccc;">
        <strong style="color:#fff; display:block; font-size:1.4rem;">777+</strong>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase;">Videos Published</span>
      </div>
      <div style="width:1px; height:40px; background:#333;"></div>
      <div style="text-align:center; color:#ccc;">
        <strong style="color:#fff; display:block; font-size:1.4rem;">Father of 8</strong>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase;">& U.S. Air Force Veteran</span>
      </div>
      <div style="width:1px; height:40px; background:#333;"></div>
      <div style="text-align:center; color:#ccc;">
        <strong style="color:#fff; display:block; font-size:1.4rem;">0 Investors</strong>
        <span style="font-size:0.8rem; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase;">Just Grit & Systems</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT I TEACH -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">From Manager to Leader</span>
          <h2 style="font-size:2.2rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">The Leadership Operating System That Changes Everything</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-size:1.05rem;">When hustle stopped working, I went deep into frameworks, systems, faith, and painful mistakes. What came out was a leadership system I now teach to help others escape the chaos.</p>
          <ul class="checklist">
            <li>Build a high-accountability, mission-driven team</li>
            <li>Run meetings that solve problems instead of wasting time</li>
            <li>Make strategic decisions without second-guessing</li>
            <li>Lead with purpose, discipline, and clarity</li>
            <li>Escape the "Operator's Trap" — stop working <em>in</em> your business, start working <em>on</em> it</li>
          </ul>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;">
            <a href="/services#leadership" class="btn btn-dark">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:4px; padding:2.5rem;">
          <span class="section-label">Personal Finance</span>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.6rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Building Wealth When You're Starting From Zero</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem;">We built a 7-figure business from a card table — no investors, no trust fund. On the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Visiontribemoney" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold);">Vision Tribe Money</a> channel, we share everything we know about money, building wealth, and creating a life on your own terms.</p>
          <ul class="checklist">
            <li>Zero-based budgeting that actually works</li>
            <li>Saving $100k on a military salary</li>
            <li>Finances in marriage — the conversations that matter</li>
            <li>Building wealth when you feel stuck</li>
          </ul>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;">
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Visiontribemoney" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-gold">Watch on YouTube</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT STRIP -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:center;">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label">My Story</span>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">I Don't Teach Theory. I Teach What I Lived.</h2>
        <p style="color:#ccc; margin-bottom:1rem; font-size:1.05rem;">I'm the CEO of <a href="https://www.taikatranslations.com" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold);">Taika Translations</a>, a veteran-owned, multimillion-dollar translation company built from scratch. I'm a husband, a father of 8, a U.S. Air Force veteran — and someone who used to feel completely lost in leadership.</p>
        <p style="color:#ccc; margin-bottom:2rem;">I've made painful mistakes. I've been broken, rebuilt, and transformed. Every framework I teach came from real-world experience, not a business school textbook.</p>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-gold">Read My Full Story</a>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1rem;">
        <div style="background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius:4px; padding:1.5rem;">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:900; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">CEO</div>
          <div style="color:#aaa; font-size:0.85rem;">Taika Translations — multimillion-dollar, veteran-owned</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius:4px; padding:1.5rem;">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:900; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">USAF</div>
          <div style="color:#aaa; font-size:0.85rem;">U.S. Air Force veteran — discipline runs deep</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius:4px; padding:1.5rem;">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:900; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Father</div>
          <div style="color:#aaa; font-size:0.85rem;">Of 8 kids — I know what it means to lead at home too</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #2a2a2a; border-radius:4px; padding:1.5rem;">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:900; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Faith</div>
          <div style="color:#aaa; font-size:0.85rem;">Christ-centered — purpose and integrity in everything</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">What People Say</span>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;">Real Leaders. Real Results.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <blockquote>"Before I started working with Jason, my life and business felt out of sync with the goals and dreams I had for myself. From the moment I began using the strategies Jason shared, everything started to change."</blockquote>
          <cite>Jake Gardner</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <blockquote>"Working with Jason has completely changed how I see leadership. He doesn't just give orders — he listens, challenges us, and makes sure we understand the bigger mission. I've grown more in the past year under his guidance than in all my previous experiences combined."</blockquote>
          <cite>Karina Romano</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <blockquote>"Jason has a way of making you feel both supported and accountable at the same time. He pushes you to think bigger, trusts you with real responsibility, and is always ready to jump in when needed. I've learned lessons from him that go far beyond work."</blockquote>
          <cite>João Vitor</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FREE MASTERCLASS CTA -->
  <section class="section" style="background:var(--black); text-align:center;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:680px;">
      <span class="section-label">Free Masterclasses · Every Wednesday</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:2.2rem; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:1rem;">Want to Learn How to Build an Unbreakable Life?</h2>
      <p style="color:#ccc; margin-bottom:2rem;">Join our free weekly masterclasses covering leadership frameworks, financial strategies, and building a life on your own terms.</p>
      <form
        name="masterclass"
        method="POST"
        data-netlify="true"
        style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; max-width:460px; margin:0 auto; flex-wrap:wrap;"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="masterclass" />
        <input
          type="email"
          name="email"
          placeholder="Your email address"
          required
          style="flex:1; padding:0.85rem 1rem; border:none; border-radius:2px; font-size:1rem; min-width:200px;"
        />
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">Register Free</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="section" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:600px;">
      <span class="section-label">Ready to Start?</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Stop Operating. Start Leading.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2rem;">Whether it's leadership, personal finance, or a full life overhaul — let's figure out where you are and build a plan to get you where you want to be.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold" style="font-size:1rem; padding:1rem 2.5rem;">Schedule a Free Assessment</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section > .container > div[style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr"] {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
